| established = 1960
| governing_body = [[Ministry of Environment (Colombia)|Ministry of Environment]]
| administrator = [[National System of Protected Areas (Colombia)|SINAP]]
| url = {{URL|http://www.parquesnacionales.gov.co|Official website}}
}}

The protected areas of [[Colombia]] are grouped into the [[National System of Protected Areas (Colombia)|National System of Protected Areas]]. As of 2018, there are 60 nationally protected areas which cover about {{convert|169,545|km2|sqmi|abbr=on}} and represent more than 14% of the country's area. <ref>https://protectedplanet.net/country/CO</ref>

== National Natural Park System ==
The National Natural Park System is divided into the following categories:<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.parquesnacionales.gov.co/portal/es/sistema-de-parques-nacionales-naturales/categorias-de-areas-protegidas/ |title=Categorías de áreas protegidas |publisher=Parques Nacionales Naturales de Colombia  |language=es}}</ref>
* National Natural Parks (''Parque Natural Nacional'' - PNN): 43
* Fauna and Flora Sanctuaries (''Sanctuario de Flora y Fauna'' - SFF): 12
* National Natural Reserves (''Reserva Natural Nacional'' - RNN): 2
* Unique Natural Areas (''Área Natural Única'' - ANU): 1
* Road park (''Vía Parque''): 1

