== Proposed areas ==
Currently there are other proposed areas for national natural parks:
* Morichales de Paz de Ariporo<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.eltiempo.com/verde/responsabilidad/home/morichales-de-paz-de-ariporo-sera-declarado-parque-nacional-_4790988-1 |title=Morichales de Paz de Ariporo será declarado Parque Nacional |publisher=[[El Tiempo (Colombia)|El Tiempo]] |language=es |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120629111342/http://www.eltiempo.com/verde/responsabilidad/home/morichales-de-paz-de-ariporo-sera-declarado-parque-nacional-_4790988-1 |archivedate=2012-06-29 |df= }}</ref> 

The following locations could be declared fauna and flora sanctuaries:
* [[Bosque Seco del Patía Fauna and Flora Sanctuary|Bosque Seco del Patía]]
* [[Serranía de Pinche]]
* [[Serranía de San Lucas]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.proaves.org/article.php?id_article=692 |title=Ecological holocaust: Serranía de San Lucas at risk |publisher=ProAves}}</ref>

== Disbanded areas ==
Some zones of the park system had been disbanded because of negative [[human impact on the environment]]:
* SSF Arauca
* PNN Manaure

