{{Infobox magazine | title = Nature of Wales | logo = | logo_size = | image_file = Nature of Wales.jpg | image_size = <!-- (defaults to user thumbnail size if no size is stated) --> | image_alt = | image_caption = Issue 59 – Summer 2016 | editor = | editor_title = | previous_editor = | staff_writer = | photographer = | category = Nature magazine | frequency = Quarterly | circulation = | publisher = | founder = | founded = 2001 | firstdate = <!-- {{Start date|year|month|day}} --> | company = | country = | based = | language = | website = {{URL|http://naturcymru.org.uk/}} | issn = 1742-3740 | oclc = }} '''''Nature of Wales''''' (or '''''Natur Cymru''''') is a quarterly [[bilingual]] [[magazine]] that covers [[nature]] and the [[Natural environment|environment]] in [[Wales]], including [[environmental politics]] and [[Conservation movement|conservation]].<ref name="naturcymru" /><ref name="whsmith" /> It released its first issue in Summer 2001;<ref name="naturcymruarchive" /> it published its 50th edition in spring 2014.<ref name="whsmith" /> In 2012 it ran a nature writing competition; the judging panel included [[Gillian Clarke]].<ref name="naturecomp" />
